Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.35,0:57:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,today.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.72,0:57:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,UI Document Browser View
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.67,0:57:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Controller provides you with a
